### ============================================================
### 03-delivery-estimates.http
### Testes de Delivery Estimator API via API Gateway
###
### Pré-requisito:
### - Executar 00-auth.http antes para salvar access_token
### ============================================================

@gateway = http://localhost:8099


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 1. Criar/atualizar rota SP -> SE
### Esperado: HTTP 200
### ------------------------------------------------------------
PUT {{gateway}}/api/delivery-estimates/routes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "originState": "SP",
  "destinationState": "SE",
  "minDays": 5,
  "estimatedDays": 8,
  "maxDays": 13,
  "source": "MANUAL_BASELINE",
  "modelVersion": "baseline-routes-v1"
}


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 2. Criar/atualizar rota SP -> RJ
### Esperado: HTTP 200
### ------------------------------------------------------------
PUT {{gateway}}/api/delivery-estimates/routes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "originState": "SP",
  "destinationState": "RJ",
  "minDays": 2,
  "estimatedDays": 4,
  "maxDays": 7,
  "source": "MANUAL_BASELINE",
  "modelVersion": "baseline-routes-v1"
}


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 3. Listar rotas
### Esperado: HTTP 200
### ------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{gateway}}/api/delivery-estimates/routes
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 4. Estimar entrega SP -> SE
### Esperado:
### - HTTP 200
### - estimatedDays = 8
### ------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{gateway}}/api/delivery-estimates/estimate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "originState": "SP",
  "destinationState": "SE"
}


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 5. Estimar entrega SP -> RJ
### Esperado:
### - HTTP 200
### - estimatedDays = 4
### ------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{gateway}}/api/delivery-estimates/estimate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "originState": "SP",
  "destinationState": "RJ"
}
